      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAXO MIGHTY (9) is a progressive colt who was ultra impressive in his first outing for the Grimson yard, working to the front from this barrier before cruising home by a whopping 35m. Could be bound for better things so can take this next step. LUV THE NITELIFE (10) suffered her first defeat in four starts when beaten 2m into second at this circuit and distance last week but that was her first appearance for nearly 14 months so the performance had plenty of merit. Draws deep but bound to be improved. BUZZ BOMB (1) is a newcomer to the McCarthy yard from SA where he has sound form including a placing at Globe Derby when last seen seven weeks ago. Readied with a trial and gets the ace draw. KEAYANG SANTIAGO (8) has been competitive of late and can feature again.",
